You have to relax.

320
00:27:09,991 --> 00:27:11,910
See you tomorrow.

321
00:27:29,636 --> 00:27:30,887
Leda.

322
00:27:30,970 --> 00:27:33,848
Is Cary in?

323
00:27:33,932 --> 00:27:37,143
He's in Minnesota
visiting relatives.

324
00:27:39,270 --> 00:27:42,315
What's wrong with him?
Has he lost weight?

325
