330
00:27:58,831 --> 00:28:02,752
Did the old man touch you?

331
00:28:02,794 --> 00:28:04,879
What does that have to do with...

332
00:28:04,963 --> 00:28:08,007
[Laughing]
Come on in, Billy.

333
00:28:12,136 --> 00:28:14,722
Here. You'll need this.

334
00:28:28,278 --> 00:28:30,530
He is in Minnesota...

335
00:28:30,613 --> 00:28:33,783
but he's not visiting relatives.

336
00:28:33,866 --> 00:28:36,035
He's at the Mayo Clinic.

337
00:28:36,119 --> 00:28:37,453
Leda...

338
00:28:39,497 --> 00:28:44,210
there's no such thing
as Gypsy curses.

339
00:28:44,294 --> 00:28:46,796
You trying to convince me
or yourself?

340
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:51,926
He came up to us as we were coming out
of La Zuppas, that place over in Milton.

341
00:28:53,386 --> 00:28:55,555
Cary was hunting for his keys.

342
00:28:55,638 --> 00:28:58,516
He never saw the old man coming.

343
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:01,686
I did. I tried to warn him,
but I was too late.

344
00:29:03,688 --> 00:29:05,106
He touched him.

345
00:29:05,189 --> 00:29:07,734
Then he whispered something
in his ear.

346
00:29:08,860 --> 00:29:12,447
Cary claims he didn't hear
what it was.

347
00:29:12,530 --> 00:29:13,948
I heard.

348
00:29:16,451 --> 00:29:17,619
