- Nothing!

367
00:30:25,270 --> 00:30:27,188
I don't believe that.

368
00:30:27,272 --> 00:30:30,149
I believe it's all your fault.
You hit that old lady!

369
00:30:30,233 --> 00:30:35,446
You were the one that hit her!
