370
00:30:35,530 --> 00:30:39,117
I wrote on the fence, but your husband
slapped on the whitewash.

371
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:41,703
He was too happy to do it.

372
00:30:42,954 --> 00:30:45,999
Have a nice stay
at the Glassman, Billy.

373
00:30:46,082 --> 00:30:47,417
[Laughing]

374
00:30:47,458 --> 00:30:50,253
I hear the food's good.

375
00:30:51,796 --> 00:30:53,798
There's no such thing
as a Gypsy curse.

376
00:30:53,840 --> 00:30:56,092
