416
00:33:20,653 --> 00:33:22,906
all you have to do right now...

417
00:33:22,989 --> 00:33:26,743
is to think about checking yourself
into the clinic and getting better.

418
00:33:26,826 --> 00:33:28,369
That's all.

419
00:33:29,245 --> 00:33:30,663
