what he was all along.

443
00:36:08,988 --> 00:36:11,741
That's funny.

444
00:36:11,783 --> 00:36:16,704
And look at you.
You finally found a diet that works.

445
00:36:18,790 --> 00:36:21,584
Whatever we did,
we don't deserve this.

446
00:36:21,626 --> 00:36:25,171
No? You ran the old lady down.

447
00:36:25,255 --> 00:36:31,010
Rossington fixed it so points weren't
even taken off your driving record.

448
00:36:31,094 --> 00:36:36,349
And I just ran the whole pack
of them out of the county.

449
00:36:36,432 --> 00:36:41,187
