451
00:36:43,439 --> 00:36:47,944
I didn't give you a Breathalyzer test.
I said I did.

452
00:36:48,027 --> 00:36:52,574
That's just the way we do things
here in Fairview, isn't it?

453
00:36:54,117 --> 00:36:55,910
What the hell.

454
00:36:57,620 --> 00:37:00,790
