- I wasn't drunk.

455
00:37:02,625 --> 00:37:05,211
Maybe there was
something else going on, though.

456
00:37:05,295 --> 00:37:08,631
- Like what?
- Never mind.

457
00:37:10,174 --> 00:37:14,846
I want to find the old guy
and tell him we don't deserve this.

458
00:37:14,929 --> 00:37:18,057
